{"tid":1696302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民賤聯電話訪問「引入海外醫生」","createTime":"2019-11-06T05:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T07:10:29.000Z","uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8cbe106847849b5b2226cef8f29ccf9f193c8eee","tid":1696302,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"頭先收到民賤聯電話訪問<br />\n比著平時嘅我可能cut撚咗佢線<br />\n但因為佢話係關於引入海外醫生<br />\n所以我就聽下佢講咩<br />\n我發現佢個訪問有啲古怪<br />\n佢由頭到尾無定義咩叫海外醫生<br />\n（我嘅定義當然係外國返黎個啲啦，但民賤聯會唔會當埋大陸個啲都係我唔知）<br />\n問題係問你有無去過公立度睇醫生<br />\n覺得輪候時間耐唔耐<br />\n而家每3年就要畀醫管局再審核一次啲海外醫生<br />\n覺得有無信心<br />\n贊唔贊成佢地做夠5年就變成本地醫生？<br />\n<br />\n如果大家聽到有佢地嘅電話訪問，盡量都做咗佢唔好嫌曬時間！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"3a8f181dea254e4e55e9c045eb0e2a1cf8af4e6d","tid":1696302,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e88b32485e0c9e1cc82abf11b99a72839244368","tid":1696302,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:57:57.000Z","msg":"自推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0f549eba04ded65e989e4523b5ff5e1d9b3aa9","tid":1696302,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"三連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1174a3dc83f5015f48ee9117753a8b8b9fe7d781","tid":1696302,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"四連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4c5b6357535fa8915d89cb277eb56d2b722129","tid":1696302,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06